<div class="row featurette">
	<div class="col-md-7">
	<h2 class="featurette-heading py-3">Create a study plan adjusted to your interests. <span class="text-muted">Linking Data Science to specialization...</span></h2>
	
	<p>The Master's Data Science in Agriculture, Food, Forests and Environment, with a duration of 2 years, allows the creation of a study plan adjusted to the student's area of interest. The course has the following structure:</p>
	
	<div class="row align-items-lg-stretch">
